      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "范陶"
      ],
      "text": "在阵前闪出了伯党小将，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003005_e00030",
      "play_id": "01003005",
      "scene_id": "01003005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "范陶"
      ],
      "text": "他赛如当年的潘安容妆。赛韦驮，赛韦驮缺少了降魔杵杖，赛吕布，赛吕布缺少了画杆戟枪。爱他的，爱他的容貌相，有话难讲，有一句，有一句衷肠话，",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003005_e00031",
      "play_id": "01003005",
      "scene_id": "01003005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "范陶"
      ],
      "text": "与你来商量：你若是弃瓦岗将奴归降，我与你做夫妻地久天长。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003005_e00032",
      "play_id": "01003005",
      "scene_id": "01003005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范陶"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，还有一出《酒醉杨贵妃》，没有串来。呵呵，险些儿忘了。哙，烦你几位当场面的老板，替我吹起来。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003005_e00033",
      "play_id": "01003005",
      "scene_id": "01003005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "范陶"
      ],
      "text": "去也，去也，回宫去也。唐明皇将奴骗，辜负好良霄。骗的奴欲火欢悦，",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003005_e00034",
      "play_id": "01003005",
      "scene_id": "01003005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范陶"
      ],
      "text": "万岁，",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003005_e00035",
      "play_id": "01003005",
      "scene_id": "01003005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "范陶"
      ],
      "text": "只落得冷清清，独自回宫去也。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003005_e00036",
      "play_id": "01003005",
      "scene_id": "01003005_s01",
